"love power" was the belgian entry for the eurovision song contest 2007 performed in english by the kmg's. it was performed in the semi-final following the estonian entry "partners in crime" by gerli padar and preceded by the slovenian entry "cvet z juga" by alenka gotar. the song failed to make the final after finishing in 26th place with only 14 points. it was succeeded as belgian representative at the 2008 contest by ishtar with "o julissi"